g style=\"font-weight:normal\"> </strong></p>\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:4pt\">@Compendium[fallout_zh-TW.Perks.HPSck8TaM6sgqU9P]{折射鏡}</h4>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">等級：2 </span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">先決條件：感知 6, 運氣 7, 等級 1+</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">你對所有命中部位的能量傷害抗性每級增加 +1。每當你獲得這個輔助能力，等級要求增加 4。</span></p>\n<p><strong style=\"font-weight:normal\"> </strong></p>\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:4pt\">@Compendium[fallout_zh-TW.Perks.7odCDXliv4LQcYfX]{跳彈}</h4>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">等級：1 </span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">先決條件：運氣 10, 等級 5+</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">如果一個敵人對你進行遠程攻擊並擲出突發區間，你可以花費 1 運氣點讓他們的跳彈擊中他們。讓攻擊的敵人受到他們自己的傷害骰。</span></p>\n<p><strong style=\"font-weight:normal\"> </strong></p>\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:4pt\">@Compendium[fallout_zh-TW.Perks.nZqvI96kJd19NJnI]{步槍手}</h4>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">等級：2 </span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">先決條件：敏捷 7, 等級 2+</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">你用任何射速 2 或更低的雙手武器（重型武器除外）進行遠程攻擊時，你對該武器的傷害每級加 1 </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\"><span style=\"border:none;display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;width:20px;height:20px\"><img style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:0px\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/mBL33PmUKXLERnTgoxO7tNLrV9ksQSW8f1Lx-XZ0KXqs608O4J-aih3-3E7i385XsPlMEnJVCFyNn_S0iQB-SuOuKQCZcPD_Djyi-Mpf1CrAQCLWU7a5mrGMlSjSO7