p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;background-color:#fff2cc;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;border:solid #000000 1pt\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;text-align:center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#ff9900;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\"><span style=\"border:none;display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;width:20px;height:20px\"><img style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:0px\" src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/XH95AGZS98i9kS3umlwjwrbdsWXPOv6G9KaA1IOs2LQeKiShHOxtnrL-LmUmXo2cmbEodykso4WUnt-Xdmque61s_n-mfg5ytQ4fWzjBvsgjqWQNXR6QS_MA8W64zDOZl_6S5iPQ\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;background-color:#fff2cc;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;border:solid #000000 1pt\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;text-align:center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">無效果</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:0pt\">\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;background-color:#fce5cd;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;border:solid #000000 1pt\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;text-align:center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">5</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;background-color:#fce5cd;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;border:solid #000000 1pt\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;text-align:center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#ff9900;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\"><span style=\"border:none;display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;width:20px;height:20px\"><img style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:0px\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/mBL33PmUKXLERnTgoxO7tNLrV9ksQSW8f1Lx-XZ0KXqs608O4J-aih3-3E7i385XsPlMEnJVCFyNn_S0iQB-SuOuKQCZcPD_Djyi-Mpf1CrAQCLWU7a5mrGMlSjSO7AxEdP1c6Yw\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;background-color:#fce5cd;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;border:solid #000000 1pt\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;text-align:center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">1 點傷害 + 傷害效果觸發</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:0pt\">\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;background-color:#fff2cc;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;border:solid #000000 1pt\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;text-align:center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">6</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;background-color:#fff2cc;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;border:solid #000000 1pt\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;text-align:center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#ff9900;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\"><span style=\"border:none;display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;width:20px;height:20px\"><img style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:0px\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/mBL33PmUKXLERnTgoxO7tNLrV9ksQSW8f1Lx-XZ0KXqs608O4J-aih3-3E7i385XsPlMEnJVCFyNn_S0iQB-SuOuKQCZcPD_Djyi-Mpf1CrAQCLWU7a5mrGMlSjSO7AxEdP1c6Yw\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;background-color:#fff2cc;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;border:solid #000000 1pt\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;text-align:center;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">1 點傷害 + 傷害效果觸發</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><strong style=\"font-weight:normal\"> </strong></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:italic;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">例子：雷射槍的傷害等級為 4 </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#ff9900;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\"><span style=\"border:none;display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;width:20px;height:20px\"><img style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:0px\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/mBL33PmUKXLERnTgoxO7tNLrV9ksQSW8f1Lx-XZ0KXqs608O4J-aih3-3E7i385XsPlMEnJVCFyNn_S0iQB-SuOuKQCZcPD_Djyi-Mpf1CrAQCLWU7a5mrGMlSjSO7AxEdP1c6Yw\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:italic;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">，傷害效果為穿透 1。當唯一的倖存者用他們的雷射槍命中時，他們的玩家擲出 4 個戰鬥骰，並將結果加起來。他們擲出 </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\"><span style=\"border:none;display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;width:20px;height:20px\"><img style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:0px\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/OUwB9aqGgDNiGo75OKbH53gX5A4SwLHvwlCgNu9P1EyoaXfkvtiNWPLoKhkVRZJk_DGgOLBdvTk2Qol6HiKh44Efzh5XYCYU3IJaFA11DIVz-JbKsfeoOFBnHs3KdwXfIJ4XmpM3\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:italic;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">、</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\"><span style=\"border:none;display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;width:20px;height:20px\"><img style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:0px\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/OUwB9aqGgDNiGo75OKbH53gX5A4SwLHvwlCgNu9P1EyoaXfkvtiNWPLoKhkVRZJk_DGgOLBdvTk2Qol6HiKh44Efzh5XYCYU3IJaFA11DIVz-JbKsfeoOFBnHs3KdwXfIJ4XmpM3\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:italic;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">、</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#ff9900;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\"><span style=\"border:none;display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;width:20px;height:20px\"><img style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:0px\" src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/XH95AGZS98i9kS3umlwjwrbdsWXPOv6G9KaA1IOs2LQeKiShHOxtnrL-LmUmXo2cmbEodykso4WUnt-Xdmque61s_n-mfg5ytQ4fWzjBvsgjqWQNXR6QS_MA8W64zDOZl_6S5iPQ\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#ff9900;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:italic;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">和 </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#ff9900;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\"><span style=\"border:none;display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;width:20px;height:20px\"><img style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:0px\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/mBL33PmUKXLERnTgoxO7tNLrV9ksQSW8f1Lx-XZ0KXqs608O4J-aih3-3E7i385XsPlMEnJVCFyNn_S0iQB-SuOuKQCZcPD_Djyi-Mpf1CrAQCLWU7a5mrGMlSjSO7AxEdP1c6Yw\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:italic;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">，造成 3 點傷害，並無視對手的 1 DR 護甲。</span></p>\n<p><strong style=\"font-weight:normal\"><br /><br /></strong></p>\n<div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-left:0pt\">\n<table style=\"border:none;border-collapse:collapse;table-layout:fixed;width:538.5826771653543pt\"><colgroup><col></col></colgroup>\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height:0pt\">\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;border:solid #000000 1pt\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">偷襲 Sneak Attacks</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">如果敵人在你攻擊之前不知道你的存在，那麼攻擊他們的難度就會降低1（最低為0），如果你的攻擊本來沒有惡毒（Vicious）傷害效果，那麼你的攻擊就會獲得惡毒的傷害效果，如果已經有惡毒的傷害效果，那麼傷害就會增加 +2 </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#ff9900;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\"><span style=\"border:none;display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;width:20px;height:20px\"><img style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:0px\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/mBL33PmUKXLERnTgoxO7tNLrV9ksQSW8f1Lx-XZ0KXqs608O4J-aih3-3E7i385XsPlMEnJVCFyNn_S0iQB-SuOuKQCZcPD_Djyi-Mpf1CrAQCLWU7a5mrGMlSjSO7AxEdP1c6Yw\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">。</span></p>\n<br />\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">如果命中對手的難度為 0，你不需要擲骰來命中他們，但你仍然可以決定這樣做，像平常一樣產生行動點和突發狀況。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><strong style=\"font-weight:normal\"> </strong></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">增加傷害 INCREASING DAMAGE</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">你可以通過花費行動點或彈藥來增加你用攻擊造成傷害的戰鬥骰的數量，這取決於你使用的武器類型。</span></p>\n<p><strong style=\"font-weight:normal\"> </strong></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">對於近戰武器（包括徒手攻擊）和投擲武器，你花費的每 1 個行動點（AP）都會在你的傷害骰池中增加 +1 </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#ff9900;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\"><span style=\"border:none;display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;width:20px;height:20px\"><img style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:0px\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/mBL33PmUKXLERnTgoxO7tNLrV9ksQSW8f1Lx-XZ0KXqs608O4J-aih3-3E7i385XsPlMEnJVCFyNn_S0iQB-SuOuKQCZcPD_Djyi-Mpf1CrAQCLWU7a5mrGMlSjSO7AxEdP1c6Yw\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#ff9900;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">的擲骰。你最多可以花費 3 行動點來增加你的骰池，最多可增加 3 </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#ff9900;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\"><span style=\"border:none;display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;width:20px;height:20px\"><img style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:0px\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/mBL33PmUKXLERnTgoxO7tNLrV9ksQSW8f1Lx-XZ0KXqs608O4J-aih3-3E7i385XsPlMEnJVCFyNn_S0iQB-SuOuKQCZcPD_Djyi-Mpf1CrAQCLWU7a5mrGMlSjSO7AxEdP1c6Yw\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">。你只能花費你在團隊池中保存的 AP，或者用你的攻擊產生的 AP：你不能給主持人產生 AP 來使用這個 AP 選項。</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">對於遠程武器，你每花費一個單位的彈藥，就會在你的傷害骰池中增加 +1 </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#ff9900;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\"><span style=\"border:none;display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;width:20px;height:20px\"><img style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:0px\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/mBL33PmUKXLERnTgoxO7tNLrV9ksQSW8f1Lx-XZ0KXqs608O4J-aih3-3E7i385XsPlMEnJVCFyNn_S0iQB-SuOuKQCZcPD_Djyi-Mpf1CrAQCLWU7a5mrGMlSjSO7AxEdP1c6Yw\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">的擲骰。你可以在槍的射速（fire rate）範圍內花費彈藥。例如，一把 10mm 手槍的射速是 2，所以你可以額外花費 2 顆10mm 子彈來增加戰鬥骰池。一把研究所的雷射步槍的射速是 3，所以你可以從核融合電池（fusion cell）中花費最多 3 點能量來增加其戰鬥骰池。</span></p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"xWJLZwu5IRU1lva8":3},"flags":{},"_id":"oiPhh4vrxzXeNB7P"}
{"_id":"tytZpdxYIhVkIuGF","name":"生存者（Survivor）","content":"<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:16pt;margin-bottom:4pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.999999999999998pt;font-family:Arial;color:#3d85c6;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">生存者 SURVIVOR</span></h3>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">你們是那些獨自為世界末日做準備的人的活遺產。你之所以能在核災難後的景觀中活著，是因為你的祖先往地底深掘，所以活了下來，並找到了足以讓人類繼續生存的社區。</span></p>\n<p><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-bf3a9f38-7fff-02be-59d4-7b46c59f1a5d\" style=\"font-weight:normal\"> </strong></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">你可能來自任何數量的定居點、孤立的庇護所或旅行團體，這些團體在從西海岸到東海岸的廢土上人口稀少。你可以來自新加州共和國，繼承 15號避難所和沙蔭市的遺產。你可以為保護他人而戰，那些被稱為義勇兵（Minutemen）或賞金獵人（Regulator）的生存者。你也可以是一個無情的掠奪者，或者出生在這些團體中，但為了恢復和改革而逃了出來。</span></p>\n<p><strong style=\"font-weight:normal\"> </strong></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">無論你來自哪裡，或無論你在哪裡旅行，建立聯繫和紮根都是困難的。生存者自然會對他人保持警惕，並且總是在尋找下一個騙子、掠奪隊伍或盜賊，以奪取他們辛苦賺來的資源。遠途旅行也很困難，許多旅行的生存者—特別是貿易商隊—在廢土的大型定居點之間移動，而不是在海岸間旅行。</span></p>\n<p><strong style=\"font-weight:normal\"><br /><br /></strong></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">特質 Traits</span></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">你可以從以下特質中選擇兩個，或者一個特質和一個@Compendium[fallout_zh-TW.Rules.O9TwSz9rDlBxk6FM]{輔助能力列表}的輔助能力。每個特質都有一個好處，也可能有一個附帶的懲罰。</span></p>\n<p><strong style=\"font-weight:normal\"> </strong></p>\n<div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"margin-left:0pt\">\n<table style=\"border:none;border-collapse:collapse;width:99.3119%\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:14.497%\"></col><col style=\"width:51.6692%\"></col><col style=\"width:33.7182%\"></col></colgroup>\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height:0pt\">\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;border:solid #000000 1pt\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">特質</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;border:solid #000000 1pt\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">好處</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;border:solid #000000 1pt\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">懲罰</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:0pt\">\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;border:solid #000000 1pt\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">@Compendium[fallout_zh-TW.Perks.FbyQcnlQ1Dl2tUxt]{博學}</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;border:solid #000000 1pt\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">你有一項額外的標記技能。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;border:solid #000000 1pt\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">當你使用標記技能以外的技能檢定失敗時，GM 獲得 1 AP。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:0pt\">\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;border:solid #000000 1pt\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">@Compendium[fallout_zh-TW.Perks.c5FuPJy1P5B8bE4e]{快速射擊}</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;border:solid #000000 1pt\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">如果你在戰鬥中採取第二個主要行動，並使用它來進行一次遠程攻擊，那麼額外的主要行動只需要花費 1 AP，而不是 2 個。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;border:solid #000000 1pt\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">你不能從瞄準的次要行動中獲益—你太急躁了。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:0pt\">\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;border:solid #000000 1pt\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">@Compendium[fallout_zh-TW.Perks.lhV2N745V97kn64e]{天資聰穎}</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;border:solid #000000 1pt\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">選擇兩個 S.P.E.C.I.A.L. 屬性並分別增加+1。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;border:solid #000000 1pt\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">你的運氣點最大值比你的運氣屬性少 1 點。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:0pt\">\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;border:solid #000000 1pt\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">@Compendium[fallout_zh-TW.Perks.9KfcW1J6DZnZXIVS]{重拳出擊}</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;border:solid #000000 1pt\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">你的近戰傷害增加 1 </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\"><span style=\"border:none;display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;width:20px;height:20px\"><img style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:0px\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/mBL33PmUKXLERnTgoxO7tNLrV9ksQSW8f1Lx-XZ0KXqs608O4J-aih3-3E7i385XsPlMEnJVCFyNn_S0iQB-SuOuKQCZcPD_Djyi-Mpf1CrAQCLWU7a5mrGMlSjSO7AxEdP1c6Yw\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;border:solid #000000 1pt\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">你的近戰和徒手攻擊在 19 或 20 時遭受突發區間，而不是只在 20。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:0pt\">\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;border:solid #000000 1pt\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\">@Compendium[fallout_zh-TW.Perks.Flx9ODxBHDstY0rM]{小巧玲瓏}</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;border:solid #000000 1pt\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">你可以在所有依賴平衡或彎曲的敏捷檢定中重新擲骰1D20。</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;padding:5pt 5pt 5pt 5pt;overflow:hidden;overflow-wrap:break-word;border:solid #000000 1pt\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">你的攜行重量是 150 + (5 x 力量) 磅，而不是 150 + (10 x 力量) 磅。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p> </p>\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:16pt;margin-bottom:4pt\"><span style=\"font-size:13.999999999999998pt;font-family:Arial;color:#3d85c6;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">廢土人 WASTELANDER</span></h3>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">選擇屍鬼或生存者起源的角色可以選擇以下裝備包之一：</span></p>\n<p><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-b9674a0d-7fff-7eb5-a81a-72cbbb4b9823\" style=\"font-weight:normal\"> </strong></p>\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:4pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;color:#980000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">僱傭兵 MERCENARY</span></h4>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">你以僱傭槍手的身份在廢土上旅行，與誰戰鬥或保衛誰。有時工作是誠實的，有時是混亂的，但當時代好的時候，你可以按準則生活，只接受正直的工作。時代並不總是好的。</span></p>\n<p><strong style=\"font-weight:normal\"> </strong></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">你收到以下裝備：</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">強韌服裝</span></li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">皮革胸甲或一個皮革手臂甲和皮革腿甲（你選擇部位）</span></li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">從近戰武器擇一：彎刀、球棒、卸胎棒</span></li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">從遠程武器擇一：10mm 自動手槍(auto pistol)， .44 手槍，獵槍，鐵管手動(bolt-action pipe gun) </span></li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">10 +5 </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\"><span style=\"border:none;display:inline-block;overflow:hidden;width:20px;height:20px\"><img style=\"margin-left:0px;margin-top:0px\" src=\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/mBL33PmUKXLERnTgoxO7tNLrV9ksQSW8f1Lx-XZ0KXqs608O4J-aih3-3E7i385XsPlMEnJVCFyNn_S0iQB-SuOuKQCZcPD_Djyi-Mpf1CrAQCLWU7a5mrGMlSjSO7AxEdP1c6Yw\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\"> 發所選武器彈藥</span></li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">一張紙條，為附近定居點的工作做廣告，提供 50 瓶蓋薪水</span></li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">15 瓶蓋</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong style=\"font-weight:normal\"> </strong></p>\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:14pt;margin-bottom:4pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;color:#980000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">掠奪者 RAIDER</span></h4>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">在廢土上，強權即正義。你從別人那裡獲取你需要的東西，並保護自己不受任何試圖這樣做的人的傷害。偶爾，你可能會和其他一些志同道合的人聯合起來，搶奪一些你們自己都無法搶奪的東西，但大多數情況下，都是人人為自己。</span></p>\n<p><strong style=\"font-weight:normal\"> </strong></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">你收到以下裝備：</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">披上甲胄(Harness)</span></li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">掠奪者胸甲和一個掠奪者手臂甲（你選擇部位）</span></li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap\">從近戰武器擇一：鉛管、撞球棍、卸胎棒</span></li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-co